{"tid":1308110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"或者可以試吓呢種方法制服打人廢老/藍屍！！！","createTime":"2019-07-11T20:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T22:17:52.000Z","uid":238546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e29e1338f8517319ce279a18aae5b642fdd09f4","tid":1308110,"uid":238546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:42:47.000Z","msg":"小弟打過一排rugby，不過身型較細粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係同樣都有機會可以撻低對面啲肥佬/大隻佬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HL8ugYc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHL8ugYc.png&h=530a8c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係好似右邊紅衫嗰位球員咁，<br />\n簡單嚟講就係可以試吓少少助跑跑向目標然後<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用膊頭撞落佢對腳 再攬實佢</span></span>，<br />\n其實總括嚟講只要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">撞向佢身體較低嘅位置</span></span></span>就可以。<br />\n唔知呢個方法喺呢種情況有冇用呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返兩位球員分別係紅衫只得<span style=\"color: blue;\">178cm同85kg</span><br />\n而對面綠色衫嘅係<span style=\"color: blue;\">188cm同108kg</span><br />\n但同樣可以撞佢落地下<br />\n<br />\n當然最重要係撻低個目標之後要<span style=\"color: red;\">有人幫手撳實佢</span>啦，仲有就係記得撳低個目標後<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好十鳩幾個男人坐撚住佢或者押鳩住佢</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大圍之前有單案就係3個男人制服一條友，最後比人制服嗰個抖唔到氣死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />制服人嗰3個仲要比人告誤殺：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B0pRl9dbf3Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB0pRl9dbf3Y&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0PUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=10793efb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B0pRl9dbf3Y</a><br />\n<br />\n當然，可以有更好嘅方法制服，歡迎講低集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後無論如何記得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不流血<br />\n不受傷<br />\nBe Water</span></span>"},{"pid":"59d75349f0aa6aa7a2729dc17936892f72a173f8","tid":1308110,"uid":6142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:45:31.000Z","msg":"認同請分享"},{"pid":"c01940d753e5e174bb5ba8e8ada09ba71f9f1c40","tid":1308110,"uid":238546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:51:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"816808fb8f2b2c859b0547c9f7839403a6c40a21","tid":1308110,"uid":238546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:51:34.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7fd94fd2409da3bb1e5b74d26d2180e93fcf404e","tid":1308110,"uid":238546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c6ebbedbf0b958c3f2b9670d723ed3853572c62","tid":1308110,"uid":238546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81a2c85481f2337db77ece7b368ff7d04daa5b8","tid":1308110,"uid":164043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:17:52.000Z","msg":"點避tackle"}]}